fields.name: Provider Name
fields.description: Identifies the provider that logged the event.

fields.name: EventID
fields.description: The identifier that the provider used to identify the event.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: Contains the version number of the event's definition.

fields.name: Task
fields.description: The task defined in the event.

fields.name: Opcode
fields.description: Numeric value that identifies activity application was performing

fields.name: Keywords
fields.description: A bitmask of the keywords defined in the event.

fields.name: Event Record ID
fields.description: The record number assigned to the event when it was logged.

fields.name: Execution Process ID
fields.description: Contains information about the process that logged the event.

fields.name: ThreadID
fields.description: Contains information about the thread that logged the event.

fields.name: Channel
fields.description: he channel to which the event was logged.

fields.name: Computer
fields.description: The name of the computer on which the event occurred.
